  <brief_title>Randomised Controlled Trial of the Effect of Music on Women Undergoing Assisted Reproductive Technology Treatments.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomised Controlled Trial of the Effect of Music on Women Undergoing Assisted Reproductive Technology Treatments.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
